submission.source: This money was saved up by my family to pay for my grandparents' medical expenses and my sister’s college tuition. My grandfather is currently in the hospital after suffering a recent stroke and my grandmother has been fighting bone marrow cancer for the past two years. Both of them require daily medical attention which has put a lot of financial strain on our family. My younger sister is also currently in her first year of university and has 3 more years remaining. I know our account had more than $100K, but it makes all the difference to have this money back to pay for these expenses.
